<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="margin: 0;padding: 0;">
<head>
    <title></title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 2px solid #FFF;">

<div style="background: #7a7a7a;padding: 1% 10%;border:2px solid #FFF;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">

    <p class="logo_name"
       style="font-size: 35px;font-weight: 600;color: #333; margin: 10px 0 10px 0;text-align: center;">
        <img src="https://www.ratingsville.com/assets/img/logo-8.png"
             style="width: 25%;position: relative;top: 10px;right: 10px;">
        <!-- Ratingsville -->
    </p>

    <div class="body" style="position:relative;min-height: 150px;background: #FFF;padding: 20px 40px;border-radius:6px">
        <h2 style="color: black;margin-bottom: 50px;font-weight:bold;">Hello <%= user_first_name %>,</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;">
             This email confirms that your review for <%= daycare_name %> was successfully submitted on <%= submission_date %>.
             We will carefully look through your review to ensure it meets our review guidelines and may contact you to resolve any outstanding issues prior to publishing it.
             A copy of your review is shown below. If you find any errors, please <a href="<%= login_link %>">log in</a> and update your review
             in the Reviews Submitted section of your dashboard or by visiting the Reviews tab for <%= daycare_name %>.
             <br/><br/>
             As always, please do not hesitate to <a href="<%= contact_link %>">contact us</a> if you have any questions.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;">
            Thank you for being a valued customer. We look forward to your continued partnership.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;">Sincerely,</p>
        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;"><b>The Ratingsville Team </b></p>
        <br/>
        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;">
            Review for <%= daycare_name %> submitted on <%= submission_date %>:
            <br/><br/>
            <span><b>Safety</b> <%- review_info.safetyStars %> <%- review_info.safetyComment %></span>
            <br/>
            <span><b>Facilities</b> <%- review_info.facilitiesStars %> <%- review_info.facilitiesComment %></span>
            <br/>
            <span><b>Staff</b> <%- review_info.staffStars %> <%- review_info.staffComment %></span>
            <br/>
            <span><b>Education</b> <%- review_info.educationStars %> <%- review_info.educationComment %></span>
            <br/>
            <span><b>Overall</b> <%- review_info.overAllStars %> <%- review_info.overAllComment %></span>
        </p>
        <hr style="border: none;border-bottom: 1px solid #ececec;margin: 40px 0 1.5rem 0;">


    </div>


    <div class="footer">
        <p style="padding-top: 20px; font-size: 14px;color: white;text-align: center;font-weight: 600;">Copyright &copy;
            2018 - Ratingsville</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div style="height: 5px;"></div>
</body>
</html>


